java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public class ViewPublication
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener

ViewPublication class is the GUI for general users to view the details of the publication they choose from the HomePage.

Users can view specific Publication which can be book, JournalPaper and ConferencePaper. Users can request copy of publication they view. This class also provide the entry for users to return back to the HomePage or login as academic staff and administrator.

See Also:
Publication, JournalPaper, ConferencePaper, HomePage, Serialized Form

Method Detail

actionPerformed

public void actionPerformed(java.awt.event.ActionEvent arg0)
This method to implement the Action Listener of different components.

For loginButton Listener When user press loginButton and correct username and password are provided. Current frame will switch to relative GUI

For requestButton Listener When user press requestButton, a request copy email will send to the author

For returnButton Listener When user press returnButton, the current frame will switch to HomePage GUI
